                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18500916-name-249" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18500916-name-249" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18500916-name-249" type="surname" value="FAULKNER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18500916-name-249" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN FAULKNER</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a <hi rend="italic">cab.</hi> The prisoner had been my horse<lb></lb>keeper about three months—on 12th Aug. I gave him two sovereigns, to go and pay my duty at the Excise-office—he did not come back—I saw him afterwards at a coach-stand, and gave him into custody.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18500916-name-250" type="witnessName">
