                        <interp inst="t18500916-name-250" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE HAMMOND</persName>
                  </hi>. I am clerk to the Inland Revenue; Mr. John Thorborn is the collector. The prisoner did not pay me 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. on 12th Aug. for Mr. Faulkner—it was paid by Mrs. Faulkner, on the 13th—Mr. Thorborn receives money.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18500916-name-251" type="witnessName">
